## \uc0\u9881 \u65039  Setup & Deployment\
\
### 1. Requirements\
* A **JSONBin.io** Master Key (for database read/write permissions).\
* An **OpenWeatherMap** API Key (One Call 3.0 subscription enabled).\
\
### 2. Configuration\
Locate the `/* \uc0\u9472 \u9472  CONFIG \u9472 \u9472  */` section at the base of the HTML file and populate your unique credentials:\
\
```javascript\
const BIN_KEY = 'YOUR_SECRET_KEY';      // JSONBin Master Key\
const WEATHER_KEY = 'YOUR_API_KEY';      // OpenWeatherMap Key\
const LAT = '41.50';                     // Latitude (Avon Lake)\
const LON = '-82.02';                    // Longitude (Avon Lake)}